headline: Invitation Homes Announces Dates for Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: DALLAS, January 21, 2026--Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE: INVH) ("Invitation Homes," the "Company," or "our"), the nation's premier single-family home leasing and management company, will release its fourth quarter 2025 financial and operating results on Wednesday, February 18, 2026, after the market closes. headline: Stocks to Watch Wednesday: Netflix, United Airlines, Kraft Heinz
summary: ↘️ Netflix (NFLX): The streaming company posted better-than-expected quarterly results, with series such as “Stranger Things” boosting viewership. However, shares dropped 6.5% in premarket trading. Netflix posted its results shortly after sweetening its $72 billion bid for Warner Bros.
